{"tid":710991,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰升溫】《環時》稱中國可打道指成分股！🤭","createTime":"2018-06-21T07:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T00:53:10.000Z","uid":13663,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e88932069ebc8d31f134d5373cb2365623033d74","tid":710991,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰越打越大，雙方戰場擴展到科技戰、金融戰。《環球時報》英文版今日發表題為「There&rsquo;s chance China might adopt hard-line approach targeting Dow Jones index giants」，指明道姓表示中國可打30隻道指成分股，令特朗普政權感受到更大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n文章列出多間道指成分股公司名稱，包括飛機製造商波音、重型工業設備公司卡特彼勒、蘋果電腦等，指其在華有龐大業務，即使中方尚未作出針對性措施，近期股價已因貿易戰影響而大跌。如果特朗普再將貿易摩擦升級，中國可以針對這些道指巨頭，用更強硬方式反擊。但文章沒有列明中方會採取的反擊方式，是否包括沽空、制裁、或禁運等。"},{"pid":"1b1e096978ccb98aefc1d14cc4ab0496e17c9e99","tid":710991,"uid":13663,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"Xi種是咪弱智人士😓"},{"pid":"69d639b26183f59069708149432305738d583bb4","tid":710991,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇topic都笑到我仆街"},{"pid":"46291c42e8b5bdee826d84a71b2223866fdf45a2","tid":710991,"uid":44454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"孔子工業平均指數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b7600525b85d9f33c087e8b22f61e7868b1d68","tid":710991,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"有d擔心Xi種仲可以有幾膠😣"},{"pid":"c85fa70572cd7b07d45130119901aad01a3e6f7f","tid":710991,"uid":81876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"A股日跌夜跌政府都未驚啦<br />\n<br />\n你打幾隻既股價who cares 比機會人買貨?"},{"pid":"b97bd4b2dfb0bc6651225560e724c1e055aee78f","tid":710991,"uid":171446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deadce83be73869a63dd724f374d2eeaf52a7be1","ti